Here are the steps for How to Sync and Get Facebook Birthday Notifications in Your Android Phones.

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d375ba879f4f23deb597ab1fa5cbbd62854a.jpeg?w=331&h=352}Step 1: Log-in to your Facebook account ‚Äì > Click on the ‚ÄúEvents‚Äù on the Left hand side menu below Messages

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d3755f871efe8ed2efe87c2e1991af5e6f3b.jpeg?w=311&h=400}Step 2: Now it will take you to Events page ‚Äì > in Events page select Settings icon which is on the Right h.and Side next to ‚ÄúToday‚Äù(See the pic below) -> Click Export

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d3751c57b4dc5a50f983dad0d0327d1920a8.jpeg?w=398&h=529}Step 3: After Clicking Export a new dialog box will pop up Like in the below pic ‚Äì > now right Click the ‚Äúexport your friends birthdays‚Äù and Click ‚ÄúCopy Link location.

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d375b914a732eb14aebc63561a02f29da728.jpeg?w=290&h=359}Step 4: Now in the New tab -> Log-in to your  Gmail account (the Google account in which you want your friends birthday to sync )  -> Select Google Calendar Like in the below  pic.

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d37509ad5a6740bcbb79733543ef5e31e857.jpeg?w=337&h=259}Step 5: Now in Google Calendar ‚Äì >Select  ‚ÄúOther Calendar‚Äù Drop down Menu -> Choose ‚ÄúAdd By URL‚Äù.

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d37539b169356bdf2e7d456cdf2bb0084d57.jpeg?w=440&h=487}Step 6: Now Dialog box will Pop-Up , in that paste the URL which you copied in ‚ÄúStep 3‚Äù.

{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d375cfc9472c7c5edb70ff05406bce995650.jpeg?w=442&h=494}Step 7: That‚Äôs it , Now your Facebook friends Birthdays will be Imported to your Google calender ,Look at the pics below for reference.
{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d3751780bafee8cc6bef4d36ae3f4c85bcca.jpeg?w=262&h=416}Step 8:
{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d375ce629a03affeca5d0a1d02934821a23f.jpeg?w=261&h=424}Step 8:
{image}{http://haptikappimg.s3.amazonaws.com/content/54a87066fb184b077942b9262d84d375cac46503268733c84e1aafa0fb512661.jpeg?w=255&h=417}Step 8:

Step 8 :Now that we have synced your Facebook friends Birthdays,Lets Go to next step which is How to get Birthday Notification alert in your Android Phone Refer the screenshots above.

Now in Your Android Phone Go to Settings -> Accounts and Sync -> Choose Google ‚Äì >Select the Gmail Account (in which you‚Äôve synced Calendar) ->Tap and Open -> Now you can see Menu(3 dotted) -> Click Menu -> Choose Sync Now
